H3.text: Who was the leader of the gang whose members included Benny the Ball ,Brain and Choo Choo. Top Cat

A4.text: Top Cat (voiced by Arnold Stang imitating Phil Silvers) is a yellow cat with a purple hat and vest who is the leader of the gang and titular character of the series.

A5.text: Top Cat (T.C.), is the leader of a gang of Manhattan alley cats living in Hoagy's Alley: Benny the Ball, Brain, Choo-Choo, Fancy-Fancy and Spook.
